messages.text: We should regroup and talk about it
That’s a crude thing to say
I know what they are, I’ve seen them before
What did you do to them, Devil?
Yes, it is I, your Devil
Yeah, I’m thinking no to that deal
You wouldn’t know a good deal if it bit your nose
I offered you good grades, friends, money and candy
I went through high school without your help
I can do college just the same
You’re only IN college because of me!
Your soul was to be payment
You chose to prove you were Devil
Well, congratulations! I don’t doubt it
I can reunite you two if you sign
I can bring back your entire class if you sign
Is your soul worth more than ALL of your classmates’?
So I didn’t sign your stupid contract, why do you care?!
A Devil is only as good as he is tough
So this is to send a message?
Once I have your soul, I’ll be redeemed in Hell
I know. I don’t know why I bother
I had dreams of being so evil
But the fiends of Hell don’t think so
My wife doesn’t even speak to me anymore
But would my soul even make a difference?
It would make all the difference
With your soul, my effort would’ve paid off
I’ll sign if you let me stay here
I didn’t say I’d sign yet
You have to promise I’m not going to Hell
Just tell all your demon friends, “Hey!”
“I got her soul but she was so scared, I took pity on her and let her stay”
“but here’s her signature so you totally know she signed”
Hmm they wouldn’t be the wiser
They’ll commend you for your mercy
You get your contract, but I keep my soul
And you also return my class
Sure you don’t want to work for me?
Sorry, I have life and stuff
Sure, but if you ever change your mind, I’ll be waiting
All will know it as I lead you to Hell in shackles!
We had a deal! You promised!
A text does not a deal make
Of course I did, I AM THE DEVIL
